main event: On September 29, 1958, two glowing objects were observed in the sky and then disappeared, leaving a crater on the ground.
interesting points: Witnesses compared the size of one object to the moon,Several witnesses reported sparks or flames in the tail of the objects,One witness stated that the object appeared to disintegrate,All sightings reported the objects moving in a straight line,Some witnesses reported the objects appearing at a very low altitude.
witness description: various civilians including pilots and observers
